OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FThe man on a mission to    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fopen up space to disability
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Former Paralympian John McFall is      
OL,6, working with the European Space Agency 
OL,7, on a ground-breaking study to see if   
OL,8, it's feasible for someone with a       
OL,9, physical disability to live and work in
OL,10, space. BBC News has been following his 
OL,11, progress as he undergoes astronaut     
OL,12, training.                              
OL,14,FIt's a test that any budding astronaut 
OL,15,Fhas to go through. But it's not for the
OL,16,Ffainthearted - or the claustrophobic.  
OL,18,FWith a clang, the door slams shut,     
OL,19,Fenclosing John McFall in the darkness  
OL,20,Fof a coffin-sized metal box.           
